title: Six Carriage Trail
description: Gracious and stately, this nearly 3 acre property is located at the end of a cul-de-sac that opens to an expansive Stone Georgian mansion, framed by two majestic sycamore trees. This home offers exceptional views of the Hudson River, Tappan Zee Bridge, and Palisades Mountains.

title: Residence 3503
description: This luxurious residence features an open gourmet kitchen with breakfast bar. The spacious master suite has a walk-in closet and a spa-like master bath with double vanity and bathtub. The powder room is appointed with a full-height mosaic-tile wall and bronze frame mirror.

title: Residence 3605
description: This 2 bedroom plus den features an open island kitchen and great room with sweeping views in two directions from the bay to Twin Peaks. The master suite offers walk-in closet and spa-like bath. The residence includes a windowed den with closet and second bedroom with en-suite bath.

title: Residence 4001
description: This corner 3 bedroom residence features panoramic views of the bay. The gourmet kitchen includes a breakfast bar. The master suite features 2 walk-in closets and spa-like bath. The 2nd bedroom features an en-suite bathroom and the 3rd bedroom looks out to sparkling views of the bay.

title: Residence 4302
description: This corner 3 bedroom features expansive windows throughout the great room with views of the Bay Bridge and city. The master suite offers walk-in closets and a spa-like bath. Bedrooms 2 and 3 are located on the opposite side of the residence. The 2nd bedroom has an en-suite bathroom and 2 closets.

title: Residence 4304
description: This corner 2 bedroom features a gourmet kitchen with island and expansive great room with city views. The master suite has a walk-in closet and spa-like bathroom. The 2nd bedroom features dual closets and en-suite bath.

title: Residence 4704
description: This generously sized 1 bedroom features a gourmet kitchen with island and a great room with sweeping views this span across Twin Peaks and the city. The master suite includes a large walk-in closet and spa-like bath. There is a beautifully appointed powder room with a mosaic-tile feature wall.

title: Residence 4903
description: This 2 bedroom ushers in guests with a spacious foyer. The windowed kitchen opens to the great room. The master bedroom looks out to views in 2 directions and boasts a windowed bathroom and walk-in closet. The 2nd bedroom has its own bath. The powder room is appointed with a mosaic tile wall.

title: Residence 5002
description: Beyond the formal foyer, enter an expansive great room and gourmet kitchen with a marble waterfall and bar seating. The great room boasts views in 2 directions. The master bedroom includes a windowed bath. The guest bedroom has its own bath and the 3rd room can be used as a den or bedroom.
